# Personal MindBridge Configuration
#
# This personal bot automatically discovers Discord channels by name - no channel IDs needed!
# Just create channels with the standard names in your personal Discord server.

# =============================================================================
# REQUIRED SETTINGS (Personal Use)
# =============================================================================

# Personal Discord Bot Configuration
DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=your_personal_discord_bot_token_here
DISCORD_GUILD_ID=your_personal_discord_server_id_here

# AI Configuration (Google Cloud 無料枠活用)
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Obsidian Configuration
OBSIDIAN_VAULT_PATH=/path/to/your/obsidian/vault

# =============================================================================
# DISCORD CHANNELS (Create these in your Discord server)
# =============================================================================
#
# REQUIRED CHANNELS (must be created):
# 🔴 #memo           - 🆕 UNIFIED input for ALL content types (memos, finance, tasks, health, etc.)
# 🔴 #notifications  - System alerts and feedback
# 🔴 #commands       - Bot command execution
#
# OPTIONAL CHANNELS (specialized input):
# 🟡 #voice          - Voice memo uploads
# 🟡 #files          - File attachment handling
#
# 🆕 MAJOR SIMPLIFICATION:
# All content now goes to #memo and gets automatically categorized by AI:
# • Financial content → 💰 Finance folder
# • Task content → ✅ Tasks folder
# • Health content → 🏃 Health folder
# • Learning content → 📚 Learning folder
# • Quick notes → 📝 Quick Notes folder
# • Everything else → 📋 Memos folder
#
# No more need for: #money, #tasks, #finance-reports, #productivity-reviews, etc.
# The AI handles all categorization automatically!
#
# Create channels with these exact names - the bot will find them automatically!

# =============================================================================
# OPTIONAL SETTINGS
# =============================================================================

# Voice Recognition (Google Cloud Speech-to-Text 無料枠: 60 分/月)
# 方法 1: API キー (推奨 - 簡単設定)
GOOGLE_CLOUD_SPEECH_API_KEY=your_speech_api_key_here
# 方法 2: サービスアカウント認証
# GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/google-credentials.json

# Garmin Integration (optional)
GARMIN_EMAIL=your_garmin_email
GARMIN_PASSWORD=your_garmin_password

# Google Calendar Integration (optional)
GOOGLE_CALENDAR_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here
GOOGLE_CALENDAR_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret_here
GOOGLE_CALENDAR_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8080/callback
GOOGLE_CALENDAR_ACCESS_TOKEN=  # Auto-filled during first auth
GOOGLE_CALENDAR_REFRESH_TOKEN= # Auto-filled during first auth
GOOGLE_CALENDAR_CALENDARS=primary  # Comma-separated calendar IDs

# GitHub Integration (FREE Data Persistence)
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
OBSIDIAN_BACKUP_REPO=https://github.com/yourusername/obsidian-vault-backup.git
OBSIDIAN_BACKUP_BRANCH=main
GIT_USER_NAME=ObsidianBot
GIT_USER_EMAIL=bot@example.com

# Environment and Logging
ENVIRONMENT=personal
ENABLE_MOCK_MODE=false
LOG_LEVEL=INFO

# =============================================================================
# GOOGLE CLOUD 無料枠最適化情報
# =============================================================================
#
# 📊 無料枠制限:
# • Gemini API: 1,500 回/日、 15 回/分 (十分な量)
# • Speech-to-Text: 60 分/月 (音声メモ用)
# • GitHub: 無料プライベートリポジトリでバックアップ
#
# 💡 費用削減のコツ:
# • 音声メモは短時間（ 1-3 分）で効率的に
# • 長い文章はテキストで入力
# • モック機能で開発時の API 消費を抑制
# • ローカル保存でクラウドストレージ費用ゼロ
#
# ⚠️ 制限対策:
# • API 制限に達すると自動的にフォールバック処理
# • 使用量 80% で自動アラート
# • 翌日/翌月に制限リセット

# =============================================================================
# GETTING STARTED
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. Fill in the required settings above
# 2. Create at least these 3 channels in Discord: #memo, #notifications, #commands
# 3. Run: uv run python -m src.main
# 4. Check the logs - you should see "Discovered channel" messages
# 5. Post a message in #memo to test!
#
# For detailed setup help, see: docs/EASY_SETUP.md
